							<h2 
		data-interaction-id="64d481a" 
		class="e-64d481a-e483a68 e-heading-base" 
	>
			Why Connect With Us?
		</h2>
								<p data-interaction-id="b3bf37f"  >
								Join thousands of students who have accelerated their academic and professional journey through our network. We connect talented students with the right opportunities, mentors, and resources.
					</p>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2230" open>
				<summary data-accordion-index="1" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2230" >
