									<h2 
		data-interaction-id="cac5b22" 
		class="e-cac5b22-c155f26 e-heading-base" 
	>
			What Our Clients Say
		</h2>
								<p data-interaction-id="bfb46df"  >
								<strong id="e-mnsfjqs4-uk8gib1">Insights from institutions we’ve partnered with.</strong>
					</p>
							Karthik combines deep SEO/SEM expertise with a rare ability to simplify complex concepts and clearly communicate their commercial value.
														Kevin Thompson
																						Executive, Strategic Planning
							A very thorough professional with excellent digital understanding. Worked with him on multiple projects—always delivers.
														Mahadevan Jayaram III
																						Sales &amp; Marketing
							Deep e-commerce expertise, strong organic &amp; paid search skills, and genuinely approachable. Profitable growth follows wherever Karthik goes
														David Lloyd
																						Chief Customer Officer, Awin
							Karthik improved our online marketing significantly—turning what felt like a 'black art' into a transparent growth driver.
														Syd Barhey
																						Principal, Five Rivers Chartered Accountants
							<h2>Your Journey Begins Here</h2>					<h5>Discover how we support your academic and career goals.</h5>					<figure><a href="#" tabindex="-1"><img src="http://educational-demo.local/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/graduation-ceremony-supplies-and-educational-mater-rlzu5x7wi47svnod6te4rxx5nxd107em4i7weojhdk.png" title="graduation-ceremony-supplies-and-educational-mater" alt="graduation-ceremony-supplies-and-educational-mater" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h4><a href="#">Admissions Guidance</a></h4><p>Get expert help navigating the admissions process for a smooth transition into university.</p>					<figure><a href="#" tabindex="-1"><img src="http://educational-demo.local/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/3d-minimal-financial-investment-business-success-c-rlzu72ksutsf2i0ahb9ptnhfsvp6evysy6x9iuu5rs.png" title="3d-minimal-financial-investment-business-success-c" alt="3d-minimal-financial-investment-business-success-c" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h4><a href="#">Financial Aid Support</a></h4><p>Access resources and guidance to make financial planning simple and straightforward.</p>					<figure><a href="#" tabindex="-1"><img src="http://educational-demo.local/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/career-ladder-3d-icon-png-download-6741820-rlzubcqbznnfyjsdh5wj6kl182ldh8ys7dww88hlfc.webp" title="career-ladder-3d-icon-png-download-6741820" alt="career-ladder-3d-icon-png-download-6741820" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h4><a href="#">Career Counseling</a></h4><p>Receive personalized advice to prepare for your future job opportunities.</p>					<figure><a href="#" tabindex="-1"><img src="http://educational-demo.local/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/3d-illustration-healthy-png-rlzug9fzoidcl8notaae7bzowiedocgbjok6g97kxk.png" title="3d-illustration-healthy-png" alt="3d-illustration-healthy-png" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h4><a href="#">Student Wellness</a></h4><p>Engage in programs that support your mental and emotional well-being during your studies.</p>										<a href="#">
				<svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 512 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M504 256C504 119 393 8 256 8S8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248zm-448 0c0-110.5 89.5-200 200-200s200 89.5 200 200-89.5 200-200 200S56 366.5 56 256zm72 20v-40c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12h116v-67c0-10.7 12.9-16 20.5-8.5l99 99c4.7 4.7 4.7 12.3 0 17l-99 99c-7.6 7.6-20.5 2.2-20.5-8.5v-67H140c-6.6 0-12-5.4-12-12z"></path></svg>			
									Get Started
					</a>]]></content:encoded>
